s/\"You must |DOUBLECLICK| the Global source in the Sources panel to set a source point before trying to clone.\";/\"コピーする前に、ソース패널のグローバルソースを|DOUBLECLICK|して起点を설정する必要があります。\";/
s/\"You must |TERTIARY|+|CLICK| to set a source before trying to clone.\";/\"コピーする前に、|TERTIARY|+|CLICK|でソースを설정する必要があります。\";/
s/\"You now have access to all AI Tools. Plus, you can easily add these tools to any of your other Studios.\";/\"You now have access to all AI Tools. Plus, you can easily add these tools to any of your other 스튜디오s.\";/
